Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.34,0:01:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊退新敵人後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.73,0:01:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪到了都柏林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.48,0:01:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為必須對聯邦高官提出抗議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.70,0:01:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也因此和長官打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.59,0:01:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而困於煙霧中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.75,0:01:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但救我們脫險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.67,0:01:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的是花.園麗小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.87,0:01:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真感激她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十四話 加美尤之聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.49,0:02:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪為何不行動?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.29,0:02:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長不在不能動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.17,0:02:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何突然停車?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.12,0:02:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很擔心加美尤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想回市鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.54,0:02:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他身體還這麼差嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.89,0:02:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.20,0:02:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,下車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車輛留給花用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.43,0:02:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪就在這山後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加美尤拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起飛準備完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.89,0:02:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不等艦長嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.41,0:02:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍後再接他好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後援MS情況怎樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各船員在幹什麼?快出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.34,0:03:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法了,伊萊駕駛百式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我駕駛ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪來引導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.62,0:03:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.49,0:03:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別無他法,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.91,0:03:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達由我駕駛\n以後的拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.94,0:03:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,別亂來,太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.32,0:03:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然和邱貝雷不同\n但沒問題的,我可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的...\n怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.13,0:03:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊駕駛米加戰車\n我駕駛百式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會代替捷度好好做給你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.05,0:03:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吉翁的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被擊落了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰駕駛的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.58,0:03:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼回事?為何是波蕾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.35,0:04:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道\n算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.08,0:04:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了,快點起飛\n正在做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何飛掉了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰指揮的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mk2!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mk2,結束你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快動阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達?塔克,抓著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都被打敗了,塔克撤退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.73,0:05:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪不會這麼快離開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和桑多拉會合在重整策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧?比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.66,0:05:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又被捷度救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.25,0:05:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天很老實呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.73,0:05:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一向都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!Mk2能動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.96,0:05:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度的替身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.17,0:05:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加美尤...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加美尤...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他跑去哪裏了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何不阻止波蕾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事出突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.41,0:06:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知何時波蕾又會變成敵人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.09,0:06:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會的\n而且醫院還沒驗出結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但正如亞當斯所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾能增強我們的戰鬥力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想讓那孩子成為正式駕駛員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.83,0:06:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.09,0:06:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裙子合身吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.04,0:06:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裙子是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.86,0:06:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很合身阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.15,0:06:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯吧,我在那裏找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.89,0:06:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼阿...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.04,0:06:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是捷度為莉娜而買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.81,0:06:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是為了莉娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許給波蕾穿比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長!軍用車正接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是聯邦軍的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先看看情況在說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.80,0:07:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是都柏林的總統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們和聯邦政府商議後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.09,0:07:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定制裁亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即解除武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.11,0:07:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無理取鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦,艦長?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是不理他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.44,0:07:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的聯邦還能什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是先快點去修理\n快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.74,0:07:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.00,0:07:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是花的車嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是花\n真的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.79,0:07:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花姐姐!\n來這邊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.18,0:07:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.59,0:07:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停車,不准通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?請讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.37,0:07:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.24,0:07:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是那艘船的相關人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那更不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那艘船都柏林才遇襲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們根本不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.79,0:08:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錯在新吉翁\n閉嘴,走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓住她!放開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開!\n住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.53,0:08:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開花,否則開火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.47,0:08:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想叛變嗎\n快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何要找亞加瑪的麻煩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.63,0:08:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先來襲的是新吉翁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這土地和其他不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有獨立自治的風氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵抗的話...\n囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開花姐姐!\n放開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.79,0:08:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是真的射了阿!\n放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.32,0:08:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個小孩竟然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.72,0:08:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思了\n洗達,冠武
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.12,0:08:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花姐姐,為何擅自離開亞加瑪\n我好寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.93,0:08:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,對不起你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加美尤失蹤了?\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.48,0:09:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他已經可以自己走路了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然能走動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.88,0:09:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但思想能不清晰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.49,0:09:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種身體能走到哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.27,0:09:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在說誰?\n不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.00,0:09:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我擅自離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.72,0:09:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然明知很自私
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.44,0:09:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但請幫我搜索加美尤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.90,0:09:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花瘦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.37,0:09:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對阿 已經用盡方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.06,0:09:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,我們去搜索了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.55,0:09:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加美尤對亞加瑪也很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.58,0:09:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加美尤是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.49,0:09:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是曾經駕駛Z高達的新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新人類?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我可能會知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得到嗎?波蕾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.95,0:09:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜那時也能感覺到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.00,0:09:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪的修理我們負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.14,0:10:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,一定要找到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.18,0:10:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.99,0:10:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查.奧雷格出動百式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.50,0:10:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,太慢了\n知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.54,0:10:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加美尤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.99,0:10:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽過很多關於你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.03,0:10:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們找到你阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.46,0:10:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達隊在出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.16,0:10:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了,我們也快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加美尤你在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.90,0:10:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好悶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.09,0:10:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.72,0:10:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長是擔心才叫你留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.91,0:10:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擔心我?\n對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.58,0:10:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是大家不是去戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.69,0:11:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而去搜索加美尤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好悶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.32,0:11:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能將要洗的衣服放在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.73,0:11:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾?怎麼了?\n波蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.35,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明往亞加瑪來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.77,0:11:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾你要去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.03,0:11:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左臂用好一點的料...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼能等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.43,0:11:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?\n還在修理中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.32,0:11:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道古利明正往這邊來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.22,0:11:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽不到嗎!波蕾!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?波蕾又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.40,0:11:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦,艦長?\n那傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.99,0:11:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾羅比波蕾,去迎擊桑多拉號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠢材...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.52,0:12:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對付桑多拉,單憑她怎麼行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.60,0:12:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是找藉口\n但我敗給了高達隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.95,0:12:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是機器或操作技術的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是[人]的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.70,0:12:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說因為對方\n是新人類才輸的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但若是操作這高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.91,0:12:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該可以對抗亞加瑪他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.27,0:12:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.67,0:12:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普通人駕駛精神力高達會失去意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.61,0:12:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,達尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不試試怎麼會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如達尼所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在戰鬥前你以敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.80,0:12:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精神力高達是很難操作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.56,0:12:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早有心理準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.10,0:12:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會打沒把握的仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.32,0:13:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且它的駕駛員早有人選
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.76,0:13:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這之前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.84,0:13:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦前方發現敵方MS,只有一艘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.76,0:13:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各船員準備\n亞里斯在自己的崗位顯露功績
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.21,0:13:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能開擴自己的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.64,0:13:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人個性型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.53,0:13:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,趁MS還沒出動先收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.81,0:13:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?想冒死衝過來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.51,0:13:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改道向右!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞控制塔就能立即瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.18,0:13:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了,好,了結你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想憑一艘MS擊沉船艦嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沉下去,沉下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.23,0:14:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mk2,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.68,0:14:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人在背後!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.73,0:14:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.46,0:14:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.88,0:14:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的聲音是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.15,0:14:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跌下去,跌下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的閃避是巧合嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣能量會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搶奪別人飛行器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.23,0:14:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這個方法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搶飛行器...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.45,0:14:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?又跳上來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不照我說的話就射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想借助飛行器?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.03,0:14:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以那個作為盾牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.80,0:15:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然明白...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.14,0:15:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想以桑多拉做為盾牌嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,注手!想擊沉桑多拉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人MS在後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.75,0:15:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!MS隊在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敢射就射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別得意!Mk2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.68,0:15:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真斗膽,Mk2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.06,0:15:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被避開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,證實亞加瑪就在前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續向都柏林前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一股作氣衝向亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備炮台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.00,0:15:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在海港方面發現敵艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.59,0:15:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻起飛,我們被瞄準了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,召回高達部隊\n快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.16,0:16:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,桑多拉接近中,立即回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但加美尤他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回來,稍後在搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了\n真氣人,竟然在此時...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.75,0:16:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,去桑多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女孩有危險,快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.76,0:16:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰?剛才的聲音...?\n女孩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.60,0:16:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然不在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.36,0:16:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,單憑這照片...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去,回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mk2的女孩有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.45,0:16:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.79,0:16:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,聽到剛才的聲音嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.89,0:16:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,他說是MK2的女孩\n莫非是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.26,0:16:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去能量會支持不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.92,0:16:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能量支持不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.28,0:16:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,投降吧,Mk2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.78,0:17:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.53,0:17:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕不會讓你阻礙大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.59,0:17:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精神力高達開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.20,0:17:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.18,0:17:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,會被那機器迷惑\n快離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.81,0:17:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.65,0:17:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭被削去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.84,0:17:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度...我被打敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mk2不動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.61,0:18:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別大意,可能是演戲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.08,0:18:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是ZZ高達的一部份\n我去對付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.15,0:18:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點,應該還有援軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,還活著嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.15,0:18:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,回答我,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.62,0:18:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女孩還沒死\n集中對付眼前敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.18,0:18:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別以為靈活一點就行\n是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.45,0:18:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.83,0:18:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度\n單憑一機太亂來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別囉囉嗦嗦,快合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.62,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不能讓他們合體!\n知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合不了體...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.85,0:19:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到右邊\n迴旋到右邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,伊萊迴旋到右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.14,0:19:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊貼追擊!\n知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.00,0:19:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼,又有新援軍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,比查!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.99,0:19:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?大家讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.61,0:19:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人交給我們,快合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.04,0:19:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道\n艾莉,伊萊,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.67,0:19:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家遠離,我要一舉殲滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.04,0:20:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休想,ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.21,0:20:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,達尼回來,一部MS太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射,粒子炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.45,0:20:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,戰鬥力下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.45,0:20:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左邊炮台被毀\n什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.07,0:20:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明大人,這樣下去不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.79,0:20:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪明明就在眼前,臭ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.13,0:20:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.61,0:20:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.85,0:20:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於走了...\n波蕾她呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾...\n捷度..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.44,0:20:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,波蕾,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能亂動她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.77,0:20:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.22,0:20:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要輕一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.08,0:21:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花...\n不可以說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.54,0:21:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道加美尤的所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.86,0:21:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍後吧,稍後吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.34,0:21:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加美尤他很溫柔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.14,0:21:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我戰鬥時他一直和我說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.74,0:21:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼那聲音是加美尤嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.79,0:21:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也聽見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.43,0:21:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,我們個個心理也都聽見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.31,0:21:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,抱起我,我帶大家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.97,0:21:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.44,0:21:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊,捷度快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.81,0:21:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.56,0:21:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿,是加美尤...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.02,0:21:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是加美尤..那裏...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.34,0:22:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是新人類加美尤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.00,0:22:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,就是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.39,0:22:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加美尤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.83,0:23:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們之所以不知道殖民衛星會落下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.25,0:23:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為地球聯邦的大人物屏蔽了消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.38,0:23:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這邊隼人先生戰死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.99,0:23:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也無法去營救難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.49,0:24:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可不是耍帥進行MS戰的時候！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.38,0:24:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ 掉下來的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.90,0:24:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加美尤也看見了！

